<h1>US Craft Beer</h1>
<h2>Summary</h2>
<p>
  In this project I set out to analyze the <a href="https://www.rdocumentation.org/packages/OHPL/versions/1.3/topics/beer">Beer dataset</a> 
  in RStudio to determine what factors make for a great beer. With the help of a multiple linear regression model,
  I measure the effectiveness of <i>style</i>, <i>alcohol by volume</i>, <i>age</i>, <i>year</i> and <i>region</i> in predicting a beer's rating.
  Finally, after processing and segmenting the data, I plot the highest rated beers in order to illustrate which regions of the country brew the best beer.
</p>
